633
00:57:58,041 --> 00:58:01,000
Oh, fuck.

634
00:58:01,166 --> 00:58:03,875
Ah!

635
00:58:04,041 --> 00:58:04,958
Ah! Uh!

636
00:59:22,625 --> 00:59:26,250
How can I...
Where am I?

637
00:59:26,416 --> 00:59:28,416
How?

638
00:59:28,583 --> 00:59:30,541
I...

639
