695
01:05:10,708 --> 01:05:13,541
He asked you to talk. So talk.

696
01:05:16,666 --> 01:05:18,333
- Did you plan all this?
- What?

697
01:05:18,500 --> 01:05:22,375
Uh, had these thugs
bring me here in a hood

698
01:05:22,541 --> 01:05:23,708
